Syria War 
Ceasefire brokered by Turkey and Russia takes effect in Syria's Idlib 
Truce in Syria's last rebel stronghold began at midnight after lengthy meeting in Russian capital 
President Erdogan says Turkey reserves right to 'retaliate with all its strength against any attack' by Damascus (AFP) 
By 
MEE staff 
Published date: 5 March 2020 17:38 UTC | Last update: 5 days 5 hours ago 
